title: Squatch51 Launches Mushroom Coffee Brand Inspired by Cryptid and UFO Phenomena
description: New coffee company Squatch51 combines functional mushroom ingredients with playful Bigfoot and alien branding to create a unique position in the specialty coffee market. The brand targets adventurous coffee drinkers seeking both novelty and wellness benefits in their daily brew.Squatch51

title: Astronomers spot mysterious UFO dubbed ‘Dudley Dorito’ 18 years later
description: In October 2008, the "Dudley Dorito" made headlines and was hailed as an important piece of evidence of alien life.
